

                     Server Creation - Node & Express
                   ____________________________________

                               Basic Command

                     1. Create package.json - npm init

                     2. Install Express - npm i Express

                     3. Install JWT - npm i jsonwebtoken

                     4. Install mongoose - npm i mangoose

                     5. Install CORS - npm i cors


                                Basic Steps
                              _______________


                            1. create a folder

                            2. create package.json

                            3. install Express

                            4. crerate index.js

                            5. import express inside index.js

                            6. create app using express

                            7. set uu port number

                            8. resolve HTTP request

                            9. HTTP response code

                                 1xx - information
                                 2xx - success
                                 3xx - redirection
                                 4xx - client error
                                 5xx - server error

                            10. JWT token - Authentication

                               10.1 token generation - sign()

                            11. Middleware 

                               11.1 Application specific middleware
                               11.2 Router specific middleware

                            12. Database Integration -

                              12.1 Install mongoose
                              12.2 Database connect via mongoose
                              12.3 Create model using mongoose

                            13. Asynchronous function resolving - promise

                               13.1 Resolve state - then()
                               13.2 Reject state - catch()   

                            14. CORS - cross origin resource shairing